
<div class="root">
  <div class="root-head">
    <h1>Mock Stocks</h1>
    <h4>A mock stock portfolio with real time updates using data from the AlphaVantage API.</h4>
    <br>
    <p><%= link_to "Login", new_session_path, class:"btn btn-sm btn-outline-light" %> to access a demo account.</p>

  </div>



  <div class="more-info">
    <div>More Info:</div>

    <ul>
      <li>Accounts are created with a $5000 USD balance.</li>
      <li>Stocks are traded by specifying ticker symbol and shares.</li>
      <li>API calls are limited per minute so portfolio value may be inaccurate for accounts with 6+ stocks.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</div>
